 梅影</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A0nh/T%E1%BB%A9-s%E1%BA%A7u-thi/poem-DU-Xoj-ZhfCDiwOq0PYG-A">Tứ sầu thi - 四愁詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A0nh/author-L37GQHbELmLdeisdE7nPzQ">Trương Hành</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Th%C3%B4i/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-linh-c%E1%BB%95-s%E1%BA%AFt/poem-VnWT9gPBhXHsog6eFUt8mA">Tương linh cổ sắt - 湘靈鼓瑟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Th%C3%B4i/author-KDKOma9Y1p2EXiiYHNKvMQ">Nguỵ Thôi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Y%C3%AAn-%C4%91%C3%A0i-thi-Thu/poem-dMgvUhW-sRBAQiAP5rPO9Q">Yên đài thi - Thu - 燕臺詩－秋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
